# Lockfiles are intentionally NOT tracked.
# The Sandbox/CI environment for this repo has repeatedly produced lockfiles
# with version pins that do not exist on the public npm registry
# (tailwindcss@3.4.59, postcss-js@4.5.0, debug@4.5.0). CI deletes any lockfile
# it finds and re-resolves from package.json, so committing a lockfile only
# creates risk of breakage.
package-lock.json
npm-shrinkwrap.json
yarn.lock
pnpm-lock.yaml
